e enhancement increases with the jet cone size.\nThe jet elliptic anisotropy $v_{2}^{\\rm jet}$ is also found to be slightly\nenhanced by the shear viscosity of the bulk medium in comparison to the LBT\nresults when jets propagate through an ideal hydrodynamic QGP medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 19:00:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-24"}
