oposed are usually evaluated in an academic context and surveys on quality\nrequirements in industry indicate unsystematic handling of quality\nrequirements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2022 10:26:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-07"}
