ments. Coalescence\ntimes due to hardening and GW emission in gas-poor non-rotating ellipticals are\n<~0.5 Gyr for the large initial eccentricities (0.5 < e < 0.9) typical of\ngalaxy mergers in cosmological simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2022 11:20:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
