 smart local energy systems (SLES). In\nthis paper we describe a way in which whole system design could be achieved by\nintegrating control, markets and analytics into each system. We propose the use\nof physical, control, market and service layers to create system of systems\nrepresentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2022 14:40:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-24"}
